<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạdẖạ trwm ạlnfs fy ạ̉qṣy̱ ạlsmạ ạlʿlyạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mādẖā tarūmu ạlnãf̊su fī
 ạảq̊ṣay̱ ạlsãmā ạl̊ʿul̊yā
 ạảẘ man̊ fūảạdī yā turay̱
 yah̊way̱ fī dẖī ạldũn̊yā

[V2]
 2- yasūʿu ḥaẓĩy mal̊jāi̹y
 lạa ạảb̊tagẖī siwāh̊
 ḥabību qal̊bī mun̊yatī
 ạảtūqu ạản̊ ạảrāh̊

[V3]
 3- ại̹n̊ kānati ạlsãmāʾu lạa
 tajūdu biạlạảm̊ṭār̊
 wabādati ạlạảʿ̊sẖābu
 wālạảsẖ̊jāru wālạảtẖ̊mār̊

[V4]
 4- fāi̹nã qal̊bī lam̊ yazal̊
 biạlrãbĩ yaf̊raḥu
 kadẖā lisānī sẖākiraⁿạ
 ại̹yãạhu yam̊daḥu</lyrics>
<author>ạsʿd ạlsẖdwdy</author>
</song>